REM android_search.duck
REM Triggers Android home-screen search and types a query.
REM Works on most Android launchers: GUI triggers home screen,
REM typing immediately opens the global search overlay.
REM Copy to: /sdcard/lab/ble/blueduck/scripts/
REM
REM NOTE: GUI (Meta/Windows key) = Android home on most devices.
REM HOME (0x4A) is cursor-home — do NOT use it here.

HUMAN_MODE ON
HUMAN_SPEED NORMAL

GUI
DELAY 1500

STRING who is watching you
DELAY 500
ENTER
